com.foreach.across.modules.bootstrapui.ui.factories

Class BootstrapViewElementBuilders

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.foreach.across.modules.bootstrapui.ui.factories.BootstrapViewElementBuilders

  • public class BootstrapViewElementBuilders
extends Object
    A helper class for creating a ViewElementBuilder for all main Bootstrap 4 components. This class should not be used directly but instead use the provided BootstrapViewElements.builders.

    For example to create a button element you can use: BootstrapViewElements.builders.button().

    Since:
    3.0.0
    Author:
    Stijn Vanhoof
